0. Find a system that makes their blacklistings publicly available.<br>
1. Send it SPAM.<br>
3. See what gets through, send more of that from those IPs.<br>
4. Tweak the stuff that didn't get through until it does.<br>
2. V1AGR4 !!<br>
5. Rotate IPs from your pool of thousands that aren't blacklisted.<br>
6. Prophet.<br>
7. GOTO 0.</p><p>
